Chapter: Type Checker Smoke Test

 A simple program that exercises the Codex-side type checker.

Section: Functions

  add-one : Integer -> Integer
  add-one (x) = x + 1

  double : Integer -> Integer
  double (x) = x * 2

  greet : Text -> Text
  greet (name) = "Hello, " ++ name ++ "!"

  is-positive : Integer -> Boolean
  is-positive (x) = x > 0

  apply-twice : (Integer -> Integer) -> Integer -> Integer
  apply-twice (f) (x) = f (f x)

  main : Integer = apply-twice add-one 40
